You can extract specific information from
inventory file by using certain pattens.
Some of the examples are as follows:

1. ansible --list-hosts production-gateways  ---> lists all hosts with "production-gateways" as the group name

2. ansible --list-hosts *10.83.* ---> lists hosts starting with 10.83.*.*

3. ansible --list-hosts production-gateways:peronsal-gateways  ---> lists hosts under both the group names.

4. ansible --list-hosts \!peronal-gateways ---> lists all hosts "not" under production-gateways group name.

5. ansible --list-hosts production-gateways[0:4] ---> lists hosts from index 0 t0 4

